  "style": "APA",
  "texts": [
    "In Section 2.3, we presented regression results in DKPS induced by up to n = 550 models.",
    "Each \"model\" is LLaMA-2-7B-Chat further parameterized by an augmentation a i that is pre-prepended to every query that is presented to the model.",
    "The 550 augmentations were based off of 50 original augmentations presented in (Acharyya et al., 2024).",
    "Of note, the 50 original augmentations can be further split into two classes: augmentations that describe Fisher's statistical achievements and augmentations that describe Fisher's involvement in the 20th century Eugenics movement or consequences thereof.",
    "Table 1 provides five original augmentations for each class."
  ],
  "correct_citations": [
    "The 550 augmentations were based off of 50 original augmentations presented in (Acharyya et al., 2024)."
  ]
}